description:
It’s Giving… not your ordinary podcast about fashion. From Street style to red-carpet looks, and social media posts, we’re tackling it all! All things messy, fun, and fashion!
Your two new besties Shea Coulee and Tiger Lily are here to keep you well informed on the latest and greatest trends including lifestyle, beauty, and of course FASHION! It’s giving…for the girrrlllzzz! So come join them for a fun filled listening EXTRAVAGANZA that will make you feel FABULOUS and kiki every week.

It’s Giving Fashion, is a Somethin’ Else Podcast & Sony Music Entertainment production.

episodes.title: It's Giving...Yellow Globes?
episodes.description:
It's here, girlies! In the inaugural episode of It's Giving Fashion, Drag Superstar Shea Coulee & her BFF Tiger Lily dish on the 80th Golden Globes, recent Drag Race runway looks, how Tiger convinced Shea to join (and win) the show, and the fashion trends that were poppin' when they met in college. Listen now to find out whose looks were hot and whose weren’t giving!


A Somethin' Else & Sony Music Entertainment production.
